In a message dated 3/6/03 6:28:30 AM Central Standard Time, 
cardhead649@... writes:


> "We'll see," Empath states.  "I have my own revenge to take care of 
> first - I'll consider your plan AFTER Hydras is dead."

She gazed at Empath. "Do you realize what you may be doing?" Pausing for a 
moment.

"Hydras is partly Galvatron.... & Galvatron WAS once Megatron. I don't know 
what Megatron he was before." pausing for a moment again. "You are walking a 
fine line there, my fellow Decepticon. Such a choice should not be so 
difficult. Or.. have these Autobot lackies softened you up?" She wasn't 
entiredly thrilled with the idea of Hydras terminated. Was far better to 
terminate those Autobots & their decendents.

--part1_104.2977eebb.2b98ca0f_boundary
